am:group:-5163901258 running ✅ — pipeline HEALTHY, blockers: none\\n\\n**Current (00:24 UTC):** All 4 crons still running. telegram:direct still done. telegram:group:-5163901258 still running. All unchanged.\\n\\n**No new failures. No new sessions spawned. No sessions died. No blockers. Pipeline stable.**\\n\\nSilent.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 427,\n            \"output\": 476,\n            \"totalTokens\": 45808,\n            \"cacheRead\": 14264,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 30641,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776212714966,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e0dec83f3941fb349f1e361e373c5\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"d58a83e9\",\n            \"seq\": 7\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: Agent Status to Lead\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776212534676,\n      \"sessionId\": \"56f4963d-308d-4c94-89a2-457d5f430fc4\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 45370,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776211909894,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/56f4963d-308d-4c94-89a2-457d5f430fc4.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me analyze the active master-orchestrator sessions from the list. I need to exclude the cron session `e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e` (this current cron session).\\n\\nLooking at the sessions list, the active master-orchestrator sessions (status = running) are:\\n\\n1. `agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e` — running — THIS IS THE CRON SESSION, exclude it\\n2. `agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7` — running — Cron: 5p Progress Report (QLHV)\\n\\n\\n3. `agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134` — running — telegram:direct session\\n4. `agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31` — running — Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX\\n5. `agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:c2d275a5-d70a-4775-a268-fecf4708f133` — done — child of ed2d0b5d\\n6. `agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ac986a8d-2425-40c7-835b-ed9b101b0bff` — running — a zombie Telegram send cron\\n\\nThe non-cron sessions showing as active are the Telegram direct session, the DTLX progress report cron, and a zombie Telegram send cron, while the subagent session has already completed. Looking at the active sessions, I've got three cron jobs running the 5-minute progress reports—one for the main session that just restarted, one for the QLHV monitor that's been running about an hour and 13 minutes, and another for the DTLX monitor that's been active for roughly the same duration. The telegram direct session is also still running.\\n\\nNow I'm calculating the durations based on the current time of 00:22 UTC on April 15th, 2026, using the timestamps from each session's start time. Let me work through the math for each active cron job to get precise runtimes. The cron:e7885813 session that was running from e2d0b5d just finished, so this current one is a fresh execution starting at 00:22. Looking at