r bug | ✅ Fixed |\\n| 6 | Cron jobs (5p progress + daily briefing) | ✅ Running stable |\\n\\n---\\n\\n**② TODAY'S PRIORITIES (Apr 15)**\\n\\n| Priority | Task | Owner |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| 🔴 P0 | QLHV BE MR !6 — Lead review + merge | Lead |\\n| 🟡 P1 | AHV Works — 13 P0 issues pending fix | Agent queue |\\n| 🟡 P1 | Stitch MCP wrapper test | Agent queue |\\n| 🟡 P1 | Update stitch-connect skill | Agent queue |\\n\\n---\\n\\n**③ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\\n\\n| Item | Status |\\n|---|---|\\n| Telegram delivery (17:40 UTC Apr 14) | ✅ Stable — no current issues |\\n| QLHV BE MR !6 awaiting review | ⏳ Pending Lead action |\\n| No active subagents | ✅ Zero overhead |\\n\\n---\\n\\n**System Summary:**\\n- DTLX BE: Running port 5555 ✅\\n- DTLX FE: Running port 3000 ✅\\n- Pipeline: HEALTHY ✅\\n- Active agents: 0\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n_Orbis 🌐 — 06:16 AM UTC+7_\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 527,\n            \"output\": 637,\n            \"totalTokens\": 21991,\n            \"cacheRead\": 14121,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 6706,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776208642698,\n          \"responseId\": \"062dfe0374f224e73bb8cb6eb49965ee\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"311e7def\",\n            \"seq\": 7\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258\",\n      \"kind\": \"group\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:-5163901258\",\n        \"accountId