}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent task is to send a specific message to a Telegram group. Let me check if there's a way to send Telegram messages through the available tools.\n\nLooking at the tools available, I don't see a direct Telegram sending tool. The tools available are:\n- read, edit, write, exec\n- process\n- sessions_list, sessions_history, sessions_spawn, sessions_yield\n- subagents\n- web_search, web_fetch\n- image\n- browser\n- memory_search, memory_get\n- Various confluence tools\n- Various gitlab tools\n- Various stitch tools\n- tts\n\nThere's no direct Telegram message tool. I should reply with the CANNOT_SEND format as instructed."},{"type":"text","text":"CANNOT_SEND: No Telegram messaging tool available in current toolset. Available tools do not include a Telegram send/post function."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":379,"output":172,"totalTokens":11577,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":11026,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776187812251,"responseId":"062daca5eb38f6849339f9f4c9083b45","__openclaw":{"id":"7b8fc739","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:planner:subagent:63bb70ce-b5f3-48d0-a236-b6cf5d8d7922","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","label":"telegram-5p-status-v5","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-planner-subagent-63bb70ce-b5f3-48d0-a236-b6cf5d8d7922","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776185050306,"sessionId":"0ca2d212-43d7-42cb-a3eb-01e64cd33376","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":11258,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776184755002,"endedAt":1776184856849,"runtimeMs":11708,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/planner/sessions/0ca2d2